<plot>Recovering from Traumatic Events tells the heroic and intensely personal stories of three trauma survivors with the help of six of the world's leading Post Traumatic Stress Therapists. This film sensitively presents insight into the impact of trauma in the survivor's life focusing on what helped or did not help during their healing process; an inspirational story of personal triumph in the face of adversity.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?457793</url></doc>
